#. <section id="vagga"><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.11" id="11"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an1.11-20:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 1"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 1"

#. </p><p>
#. VAR: nīvaraṇappahāṇavaggo (bj) | nīvaraṇavagga (pts1)
msgctxt "an1.11-20:0.2"
msgid "2. Nīvaraṇappahānavagga"
msgstr "2. Giving Up the Hindrances"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an1.11-20:0.3"
msgid "11"
msgstr "11"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli1.3"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc11.1"></a>
msgctxt "an1.11-20:11.1.1"
msgid ""
"“Nāhaṃ, bhikkhave, aññaṃ ekadhammampi samanupassāmi yena anuppanno vā "
"kāmacchando uppajjati uppanno vā kāmacchando bhiyyobhāvāya vepullāya "
"saṃvattati yathayidaṃ, bhikkhave, subhanimittaṃ."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, I do not see a single thing that gives rise to sensual desire, "
"or, when it has arisen, makes it increase and grow like the aspect of beauty."

msgctxt "an1.11-20:11.1.2"
msgid ""
"Subhanimittaṃ, bhikkhave, ayoniso manasi karoto anuppanno ceva kāmacchando "
"uppajjati uppanno ca kāmacchando bhiyyobhāvāya vepullāya saṃvattatī”ti."
msgstr ""
"When you attend improperly to the aspect of beauty, sensual desire arises, "
"and once arisen it increases and grows.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.11-20:11.1.3"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.12" id="12"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.11-20:11.1.4"
msgid "12"
msgstr "12"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc12.1"></a>
msgctxt "an1.11-20:12.1.1"
msgid ""
"“Nāhaṃ, bhikkhave, aññaṃ ekadhammampi samanupassāmi yena anuppanno vā "
"byāpādo uppajjati uppanno vā byāpādo bhiyyobhāvāya vepullāya saṃvattati "
"yathayidaṃ, bhikkhave, paṭighanimittaṃ."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, I do not see a single thing that gives rise to ill will, or, "
"when it has arisen, makes it increase and grow like the aspect of repulsion."

msgctxt "an1.11-20:12.1.2"
msgid ""
"Paṭighanimittaṃ, bhikkhave, ayoniso manasi karoto anuppanno ceva byāpādo "
"uppajjati uppanno ca byāpādo bhiyyobhāvāya vepullāya saṃvattatī”ti."
msgstr ""
"When you attend improperly to the aspect of repulsion, ill will arises, and "
"once arisen it increases and grows.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.11-20:12.1.3"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.13" id="13"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.11-20:12.1.4"
msgid "13"
msgstr "13"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc13.1"></a>
#. VAR: thinamiddhaṃ → thīnamiddhaṃ (bj, s1-3, km, pts1)
#. VAR: tandī → tandi (s1-3, mr)
#. VAR: vijambhitā → vijambhikā (bj, s1-3, km, pts1)
msgctxt "an1.11-20:13.1.1"
msgid ""
"“Nāhaṃ, bhikkhave, aññaṃ ekadhammampi samanupassāmi yena anuppannaṃ vā "
"thinamiddhaṃ uppajjati uppannaṃ vā thinamiddhaṃ bhiyyobhāvāya vepullāya "
"saṃvattati yathayidaṃ, bhikkhave, arati tandī vijambhitā bhattasammado "
"cetaso ca līnattaṃ."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, I do not see a single thing that gives rise to dullness and "
"drowsiness, or, when they have arisen, makes them increase and grow like "
"discontent, sloth, yawning, sleepiness after eating, and mental sluggishness."

msgctxt "an1.11-20:13.1.2"
msgid ""
"Līnacittassa, bhikkhave, anuppannañceva thinamiddhaṃ uppajjati uppannañca "
"thinamiddhaṃ bhiyyobhāvāya vepullāya saṃvattatī”ti."
msgstr ""
"When you have a sluggish mind, dullness and drowsiness arise, and once "
"arisen they increase and grow.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.11-20:13.1.3"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.14" id="14"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.11-20:13.1.4"
msgid "14"
msgstr "14"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc14.1"></a>
msgctxt "an1.11-20:14.1.1"
msgid ""
"“Nāhaṃ, bhikkhave, aññaṃ ekadhammampi samanupassāmi yena anuppannaṃ vā "
"uddhaccakukkuccaṃ uppajjati uppannaṃ vā uddhaccakukkuccaṃ bhiyyobhāvāya "
"vepullāya saṃvattati yathayidaṃ, bhikkhave, cetaso avūpasamo."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, I do not see a single thing that gives rise to restlessness and "
"remorse, or, when they have arisen, makes them increase and grow like an "
"unsettled mind."

msgctxt "an1.11-20:14.1.2"
msgid ""
"Avūpasantacittassa, bhikkhave, anuppannañceva uddhaccakukkuccaṃ uppajjati "
"uppannañca uddhaccakukkuccaṃ bhiyyobhāvāya vepullāya saṃvattatī”ti."
msgstr ""
"When you have no peace of mind, restlessness and remorse arise, and once "
"arisen they increase and grow.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.11-20:14.1.3"
msgid "Catutthaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.15" id="15"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.11-20:14.1.4"
msgid "15"
msgstr "15"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli1.4"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc15.1"></a>
msgctxt "an1.11-20:15.1.1"
msgid ""
"“Nāhaṃ, bhikkhave, aññaṃ ekadhammampi samanupassāmi yena anuppannā vā "
"vicikicchā uppajjati uppannā vā vicikicchā bhiyyobhāvāya vepullāya "
"saṃvattati yathayidaṃ, bhikkhave, ayonisomanasikāro."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, I do not see a single thing that gives rise to doubt, or, when "
"it has arisen, makes it increase and grow like improper attention."

msgctxt "an1.11-20:15.1.2"
msgid ""
"Ayoniso, bhikkhave, manasi karoto anuppannā ceva vicikicchā uppajjati "
"uppannā ca vicikicchā bhiyyobhāvāya vepullāya saṃvattatī”ti."
msgstr ""
"When you attend improperly, doubt arises, and once arisen it increases and "
"grows.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.11-20:15.1.3"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.16" id="16"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.11-20:15.1.4"
msgid "16"
msgstr "16"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc16.1"></a>
msgctxt "an1.11-20:16.1.1"
msgid ""
"“Nāhaṃ, bhikkhave, aññaṃ ekadhammampi samanupassāmi yena anuppanno vā "
"kāmacchando nuppajjati uppanno vā kāmacchando pahīyati yathayidaṃ, "
"bhikkhave, asubhanimittaṃ."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, I do not see a single thing that prevents sensual desire from "
"arising, or, when it has arisen, abandons it like the aspect of ugliness."

msgctxt "an1.11-20:16.1.2"
msgid ""
"Asubhanimittaṃ, bhikkhave, yoniso manasi karoto anuppanno ceva kāmacchando "
"nuppajjati uppanno ca kāmacchando pahīyatī”ti."
msgstr ""
"When you attend properly to the aspect of ugliness, sensual desire does not "
"arise, or, if it’s already arisen, it’s given up.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.11-20:16.1.3"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.17" id="17"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.11-20:16.1.4"
msgid "17"
msgstr "17"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc17.1"></a>
msgctxt "an1.11-20:17.1.1"
msgid ""
"“Nāhaṃ, bhikkhave, aññaṃ ekadhammampi samanupassāmi yena anuppanno vā "
"byāpādo nuppajjati uppanno vā byāpādo pahīyati yathayidaṃ, bhikkhave, mettā "
"cetovimutti."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, I do not see a single thing that prevents ill will from "
"arising, or, when it has arisen, abandons it like the heart’s release by "
"love."

msgctxt "an1.11-20:17.1.2"
msgid ""
"Mettaṃ, bhikkhave, cetovimuttiṃ yoniso manasi karoto anuppanno ceva byāpādo "
"nuppajjati uppanno ca byāpādo pahīyatī”ti."
msgstr ""
"When you attend properly on the heart’s release by love, ill will does not "
"arise, or, if it’s already arisen, it’s given up.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.11-20:17.1.3"
msgid "Sattamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.18" id="18"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.11-20:17.1.4"
msgid "18"
msgstr "18"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc18.1"></a>
msgctxt "an1.11-20:18.1.1"
msgid ""
"“Nāhaṃ, bhikkhave, aññaṃ ekadhammampi samanupassāmi yena anuppannaṃ vā "
"thinamiddhaṃ nuppajjati uppannaṃ vā thinamiddhaṃ pahīyati yathayidaṃ, "
"bhikkhave, ārambhadhātu nikkamadhātu parakkamadhātu."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, I do not see a single thing that prevents dullness and "
"drowsiness from arising, or, when they have arisen, by which they are given "
"up like the elements of initiative, persistence, and vigor."

msgctxt "an1.11-20:18.1.2"
msgid ""
"Āraddhavīriyassa, bhikkhave, anuppannañceva thinamiddhaṃ nuppajjati "
"uppannañca thinamiddhaṃ pahīyatī”ti."
msgstr ""
"When you’re energetic, dullness and drowsiness do not arise, or, if they’ve "
"already arisen, they’re given up.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.11-20:18.1.3"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.19" id="19"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.11-20:18.1.4"
msgid "19"
msgstr "19"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc19.1"></a>
msgctxt "an1.11-20:19.1.1"
msgid ""
"“Nāhaṃ, bhikkhave, aññaṃ ekadhammampi samanupassāmi yena anuppannaṃ vā "
"uddhaccakukkuccaṃ nuppajjati uppannaṃ vā uddhaccakukkuccaṃ pahīyati "
"yathayidaṃ, bhikkhave, cetaso vūpasamo."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, I do not see a single thing that prevents restlessness and "
"remorse from arising, or, when they have arisen, by which they are given up "
"like peace of mind."

msgctxt "an1.11-20:19.1.2"
msgid ""
"Vūpasantacittassa, bhikkhave, anuppannañceva uddhaccakukkuccaṃ nuppajjati "
"uppannañca uddhaccakukkuccaṃ pahīyatī”ti."
msgstr ""
"When your mind is peaceful, restlessness and remorse do not arise, or, if "
"they’ve already arisen, they’re given up.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.11-20:19.1.3"
msgid "Navamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.20" id="20"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.11-20:19.1.4"
msgid "20"
msgstr "20"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli1.5"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc20.1"></a>
msgctxt "an1.11-20:20.1.1"
msgid ""
"“Nāhaṃ, bhikkhave, aññaṃ ekadhammampi samanupassāmi yena anuppannā vā "
"vicikicchā nuppajjati uppannā vā vicikicchā pahīyati yathayidaṃ, bhikkhave, "
"yonisomanasikāro."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, I do not see a single thing that prevents doubt from arising, "
"or, when it has arisen, gives it up like proper attention."

msgctxt "an1.11-20:20.1.2"
msgid ""
"Yoniso, bhikkhave, manasi karoto anuppannā ceva vicikicchā nuppajjati "
"uppannā ca vicikicchā pahīyatī”ti."
msgstr ""
"When you attend properly, doubt does not arise, or, if it’s already arisen, "
"it’s given up.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.11-20:20.1.3"
msgid "Dasamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.11-20:20.1.4"
msgid "Nīvaraṇappahānavaggo dutiyo."
msgstr ""
